# This file explains the structure of this repository, explaining the contents and behaviour of all Units

# /Gui
# -> main.py
#     runs the gui application, as well as all app mechanics

# -> pages.py
#     declares the two most important pages of the application, including some additional methods to setup the editor page from a file path
#     -> Editor::setup_root() # NOTE: DO NOT USE THIS METHOD OUTSIDE OF THE EDITOR PAGE (its meant to be prevent code duplications, as a member, within the class)
#         sets up the root layout of the editor page, clearing all previous widgets and setting up the canvas